THQ Nordic: First comment Q2, crushing it [https://www.redeye.se/company/thq-nordic/580787/thq-nordic-first-comment-q2-crushing-it?utm_source=note&utm_medium=email] profil analyst [http://res.cloudinary.com/redeye/image/upload/c_thumb,g_face:center,h_60,q_auto:best,w_60,z_0.6/v1/Redeye%20Employees/Kristoffer_Lindstr%C3%B6m_xetpul] 

